title: My 10 Books - January 2016 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 10 books. mostly ePUBs, for this month:

01. Brief Candle in the Dark - My Life in Science by Richard Dawkins
02. Fire Mission - The Diary of a Firing Sergeant in Afghanistan by Craig Douglas
03. Flower Power - Lessons from the Los Angeles School of Flower Design by Michael Gaffney
04. Fraud Analytics - Using Descriptive, Predictive, and Social Network Techniques by Bart Baesens
05. Growing Vegetables West of the Cascades - The Complete Guide to Organic Gardening (35th Anniversary Ed) by Steve Solomon,Marina McShane
06. How a Computer Works by Camboard Technology
07. How Consciousness Became the Universe by Chopra, Deepak
08. Marie Curie and Her Daughters - The Private Lives of Science's First Family by Shelley Emling
09. My Gita by Devdutt Pattanaik
10. Physics - A short history from quintessence to quarks by John L. Heilbron
